a:3:{s:4:"time";i:1773037810;s:3:"ttl";i:86400;s:4:"data";a:5:{s:5:"title";s:60:"LlamaFactory训练平台使用及本地部署 - 博客系统";s:4:"post";a:23:{s:2:"id";s:2:"16";s:5:"title";s:45:"LlamaFactory训练平台使用及本地部署";s:4:"slug";s:45:"llamafactory训练平台使用及本地部署";s:7:"content";s:1750:"<p><strong>安装工具和依赖（py虚拟环境处理）</strong><br>git clone --depth 1 https://github.com/hiyouga/LLaMA-Factory.git </p><p>cd LLaMA-Factory </p><p>pip install -e . </p><p>pip install -r requirements/metrics.txt</p><p><strong>执行启动命令</strong></p><p>llamafactory-cli webui --use-cpu</p><p> </p><h2>使用 Ollama 部署</h2><p>官方文档：https://docs.ollama.com/ </p><p>首先需要克隆项目并安装依赖：</p><p>git clonehttps://github.com/ggerganov/llama.cpp.git </p><p>cd llama.cpp </p><p>pip install -r requirements.txt</p><p><strong>1. 模型格式转换 (HF -&gt; GGUF)</strong></p><p><strong>$ python convert_hf_to_gguf.py [模型路径] --outfile [输出路径/model.gguf] </strong></p><p><strong>2. 使用 Ollama 启动服务 </strong></p><p><strong>修改 Modelfile 配置后，执行以下命令启动： $ ollama create &lt;model-name&gt; -f Modelfile </strong></p><p><strong>$ ollama run &lt;model-name&gt;</strong></p><figure class="image"><img style="aspect-ratio:559/374;" src="/uploads/20260309/20260309_895df34c7e5c4a15.png" width="559" height="374"></figure><p><strong> </strong>  </p><p> </p><p> </p><h2>Python API调用示例</h2><p>from  ollama  import  chat, ChatResponse </p><p> response = chat(model='qwen_self', messages=[{ 'role':'user','content':'飞机上可做的五件事' }]) </p><p> print(response['message']['content'])</p><figure class="image image-style-align-left"><img style="aspect-ratio:549/412;" src="/uploads/20260309/20260309_d8b3377c8b59efbe.png" width="549" height="412"></figure><figure class="image image-style-align-left"><img style="aspect-ratio:1218/561;" src="/uploads/20260309/20260309_850783070af018bd.png" width="1218" height="561"></figure><p> </p><p>  </p>";s:7:"excerpt";s:6:"示例";s:14:"featured_image";N;s:7:"user_id";s:1:"1";s:11:"category_id";s:1:"3";s:6:"status";s:9:"published";s:10:"visibility";s:6:"public";s:5:"views";s:1:"1";s